text: Mangromedes is a genus of spiders in the family Pisauridae. ==Species== , the World Spider Catalog accepted the following extant species: *Mangromedes kochi (Roewer, 1951) type species – Australia (Queensland) *Mangromedes porosus Raven & Hebron, 2018 – Australia (Northern Territory) ==References== Category:Pisauridae Category:Araneomorphae genera
title: Mangromedes
